{"tid":2014930,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam 2020年4月玩家硬體使用統計出爐 AMD市佔率提升至21.89％","createTime":"2020-05-13T10:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T09:33:33.000Z","uid":32511,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"edeb965bc9d7ea25ea781c38e7c34183ec00ef15","tid":2014930,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/jtbvnJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FjtbvnJo.jpg&h=b4c3b67c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSteam 遊戲平台公布 2020 年 4 月硬體 &amp; 軟體調查， 雖然 CPU 處理器仍是 Intel 英特爾獨佔鰲頭，但 AMD CPU 處理器的市佔率再度提升，從原本的 19% 提升至21.89%，而進一步查看處理器的統計資料，多數玩家使用 4 核心處理器。至於系統部分，超過95.06% 玩家都使用 Windows 作業系統在 Steam 遊戲，macOS 系統則是只有 4.05%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/kFjHUqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FkFjHUqA.jpg&h=e2724e2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n顯示卡部分，NVIDIA 以 73.28% 擊敗各家品牌，其中又以 NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1060 顯示卡最受歡迎，其次則是 NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050 Ti 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/rmH8u68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FrmH8u68.jpg&h=32b88965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，如果想體驗 VR 虛擬實境遊戲的玩家，HTC VIVE 頭戴顯示器以 26.07% 成為市佔率最高的 VR 顯示器，然而由於 VR 顯示器製造商愈來愈多，也擠壓了不少原來知名廠商的市佔率，也因此包括 WINDOWS MIXED REALITY、VALVE INDEX HMD、OCULUS RIFT、<br />\nOCULUS RIFT S、HTC VIVE &hellip;等都有略有起伏。"},{"pid":"01878acb1e7190429cd86fa33c2c4410105843a5","tid":2014930,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"我cpu gpu都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee7e14b08c318c2c872e756e022ea0c298f638f","tid":2014930,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:26:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">AMD yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望OpenCL 返嚟</span>"},{"pid":"0e2806ec6